<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Happy Birthday Sabnoor</title>
<style>
body{margin:0;font-family:Verdana;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#14001f,#2a0055,#06142e);color:#fff;overflow-x:hidden}
.stars{position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(white 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:50px 50px;opacity:.35}
.card{max-width:900px;margin:60px auto;padding:35px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-radius:25px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px #000;transform:perspective(900px) rotateX(5deg)}
h1{text-align:center;color:#ff99d6}button{display:block;margin:20px auto;padding:15px 28px;border-radius:30px;border:0;background:#ff4d94;color:#fff;font-size:20px}
#letter{display:none;line-height:1.9;font-size:18px} .heart{position:fixed;font-size:24px;animation:f 6s linear forwards}@keyframes f{from{transform:translateY(-10vh)}to{transform:translateY(110vh)}}
</style></head><body><div class="stars"></div><div class="card"><h1>🎂 Happy Birthday Meri Pyari Sabnoor ❤️</h1><button onclick="o()">💖 Surprise Open Karo 💖</button><div id="letter"><br># 🎂 Happy Birthday Meri Pyari Sabnoor ❤️<br><br>**Tumhare Ahsan ki taraf se...**<br><br>Meri Pyari Sabnoor,<br><br>Aaj ka din mere liye bhi utna hi khaas hai jitna tumhare liye, kyunki aaj us insaan ka janamdin hai jisne meri zindagi ko khushiyon se bhar diya.<br><br>Yaqeen hi nahi hota ki hamare saath ko 2 saal ho gaye. In 2 saalon mein tumne mujhe itni khushiyan di hain ki unhe lafzon mein bayan karna mushkil hai.<br><br>Tumhari muskurahat meri sabse badi taqat hai. Jab bhi main pareshan hota hoon, tumhari ek baat ya ek muskurahat mera din behtar bana deti hai.<br><br>Main Allah se dua karta hoon ki tum hamesha khush raho, sehatmand raho, har sapna tumhara poora ho aur tumhari zindagi hamesha khushiyon se bhari rahe.<br><br>Main tumse ek wada karta hoon ki chahe zindagi mein kitni bhi mushkilein aayein, main hamesha tumhara saath dunga aur har khushi aur har gham mein tumhare saath khada rahunga.<br><br>Shukriya meri zindagi mein aane ke liye.<br>Shukriya mujhe itna pyaar dene ke liye.<br><br>❤️ Happy Birthday Meri Jaan, Meri Sabnoor.<br><br>Allah tumhari har dua qubool kare aur hamesha tumhe apni hifazat mein rakhe.<br><br>Main tumse bahut mohabbat karta hoon... aur hamesha karta rahunga. ❤️<br><br>Hamesha Tumhara,<br><br>Ahsan ❤️<br></div></div>
<script>
function o(){document.getElementById('letter').style.display='block';for(let i=0;i<100;i++){let d=document.createElement('div');d.className='heart';d.innerHTML=Math.random()>0.5?'💖':'❤️';d.style.left=Math.random()*100+'vw';d.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*4)+'s';document.body.appendChild(d);}}
</script></body></html>
